🏠 OUR FAMILY CALENDAR APP 📅
================================

Hey there! Welcome to our super cool Family Calendar! 🎉

WHAT IS THIS? 🤔
----------------
You know how sometimes Dad forgets about your soccer practice, 
or Mom asks "What should we have for dinner?" like 100 times?

Well, this app fixes ALL of that! It's like a magic board where 
our whole family can see:
  ✓ What's happening each day
  ✓ What yummy food we're eating
  ✓ What groceries we need to buy
  ✓ WHO likes what food! 👍👎

NEW! LOGGING IN 🔐
------------------
Now everyone has their own account!

1. Open the app and you'll see the PRETTY RAINBOW LOGIN SCREEN! 🌈
2. Click on YOUR profile picture (Dad, Mom, or You!)
3. Type the secret PIN: **6565** (shhh, don't tell anyone!)
4. You're in! 🎉

Your name shows at the top so everyone knows who's using the app!

WHAT CAN YOU DO? 🎮
-------------------

📅 THE CALENDAR
   - See everyone's stuff on one calendar
   - Dad's meetings = BLUE 🔵
   - Mom's stuff = RED 🔴 
   - Your activities = GREEN 🟢
   - Click on any day to add something new!
   - See a little 🍲 icon? Click it to see what's for dinner!

🍽️ MEAL PLANNER
   - Pick what we eat for:
     🌅 Breakfast (morning food!)
     🌤️ Lunch (noon munchies!)
     🍪 Snack (yay snacks!)
     🌙 Dinner (family time food!)
   - No more "I don't know what to eat" 
   
   NEW! 👍👎 VOTING ON MEALS!
   - See a meal? Click 👍 if you LIKE it!
   - Click 👎 if you don't... (but be nice!)
   - See who voted with their little avatar pictures!
   - You can only vote once per meal (no cheating!)

🛒 GROCERY LIST
   - The app makes a shopping list FROM the meals!
   - Check off items at the store
   - Never forget the good snacks again!

📱 ON YOUR PHONE
   - Works great on phones too!
   - See the buttons at the bottom? 
   - Tap them to switch between Calendar, Meals, and Grocery!
   - The big ➕ button adds new stuff!

HOW TO START IT? 🚀
-------------------
1. Ask a grown-up to open the terminal (the black screen with typing)
2. Type: npm install (this downloads helper stuff - like getting ingredients)
3. Type: npm run dev (this turns on the app!)
4. Go to: http://localhost:3000 in your browser
5. Pick your name on the rainbow screen! 🌈
6. Enter the PIN: 6565
7. BOOM! You're in! 💥

WHO'S IN OUR FAMILY? 👨‍👩‍👧
--------------------------
Right now the app has:
  🔵 Parent 1 (Blue)
  🔴 Parent 2 (Red)
  🟢 Child - that's YOU! (Green)

(A grown-up can change the names in the Settings ⚙️!)

THE COOL PART 🌟
----------------
If we set up something called "Firebase" (it's free!), 
EVERYONE in the family can see the same calendar from 
their own phone or computer. Like magic! ✨

Without Firebase, it only works on one device - still cool though!

IT'S SO PRETTY! 🌈
------------------
Did you notice the rainbow colors moving in the background?
That's called a "gradient animation" - it makes the app 
look like a magical rainbow! The buttons are purple and glow
when you touch them. Cool, right?

TO LOG OUT 🚪
-------------
See the door emoji 🚪 at the top right?
Click it to log out and let someone else use the app!

